
---

# ✅ **.gitignore**
Save as: **.gitignore**

```gitignore
# Dataset (do not upload)
dataset/
data/train/
data/valid/
data/test/

# YOLO training outputs
runs/
shape_train_cpu/
shape_train_gpu/
shape_train_main/
logs/

# Python cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# Model files (except small ones)
*.pt
*.pth
*.onnx
*.h5

# Videos
*.mp4
*.avi
*.mkv
*.mov

# OS / Editor junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/

# Environment
env/
venv/
*.egg-info
